{
  "texts": [
    "One image per unique page was selected in the intermediate set.",
    "Given that molecules from the same page are likely to be similar, this strategy increases the diversity of molecules in the set.",
    "Then, images were sampled according to the uniform distribution over year slices and offices computed from the intermediate set.",
    "Finally, we built the D2C-RND dataset.",
    "From the intermediate set, images were randomly sampled following the number of images per office estimated in PatCID."
  ]
}